               <msContents>
                  <summary>Book of Marriage Ritual (lit. Crowning), መጽሐፈ፡ ተክሊል፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="33r" facs="002">Fols 1r–33r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1970Mashaf">Maṣḥafa
                                                  taklil</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> እጽሕፍ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ተክሊል፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ሕገ፡ ሰብሳብ፡ ወዝውእቱ፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በላዕለ፡ አልባሳት፡ ዘመርዓዊ፡ ወመርዓት፡ ወእምዝ፡ ይቤሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ ተሣሃለነ፡ አምላክነ፡ ኃያል፡ ወኵን፡ ምስሌነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ እስመ፡ ረዳኢነ፡ ጊዜ፡ ምንዳቤነ፡ ዘእንበሌከ፡ አልብነ፡</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                       <locus target="#33r" facs="034">Fol. 33r</locus>
                       <q>“Here ends the Book of Crowning, by the peace of God, 1952, EC.”</q>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
